values: Ok,well here's how it's going down Sunday I went to my little brother's games and his team won both and then on monday I was feeling bad so I didn't go to school and I went to the doctor and they said that I have the flu so I have just been layin around watching TV and eating popsicles for like 3 days and it has been totally boring and I can't go back to school like monday, and I definitely can't play in the soccer games this weekend and I think that is the worst part. The other sad thing that has happened lately is that Whitney is gonna move back to florida like really soon as I'm writing this she is probably like packing her stuff to go back to Florida! Gonna miss you Whit!

I like always forget to write in these things, but anyways this week was good to school n then Me n Maria went to work out same thing on tuesday, then on wednesday i had soccer with EV which was fun n everyone likes him so thats cool, thursday i went to school n did homework and friday i had school again wow! we have that 2 much n then Leann came over so we hung out n then we had a game this mornin n Cookville so i had to wake up at like 7 and drive a long way n then the game was @ 10:30 and we won 2-0 which was ok because we had only one practice, and tonight I think that Me and Galley are gonna go play some pool. THat is my week and it is probably perty borin n I'm sry
